msgstr "完全損壞"

#: .\a_materials.json .\comestibles.json
msgid "koji"
msgid_plural "koji"
msgstr[0] "曲"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soybean"
msgid_plural "soybeans"
msgstr[0] "大豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soybean', 'str_pl': 'soybeans'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Soybeans. These are indispensable in the Japanese diet."
msgstr "大豆。這是日本飲食中不可或缺的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "edamame"
msgid_plural "edamame"
msgstr[0] "毛豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'edamame', 'str_pl': 'edamame'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "An immature soybean. Tastes good on it's own."
msgstr "未成熟的大豆。本身味道不錯。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soybean seed"
msgid_plural "soybean seeds"
msgstr[0] "大豆種子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soybean seed', 'str_pl': 'soybean seeds'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"It is a soybean seed. If you have a flower pot, you can plant it to harvest "
"it in the form of edamame."
msgstr "這是一顆大豆種子。如果你有花盆，可以種植它以收穫毛豆。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soy sauce (unfermented)"
msgid_plural "soy sauce (unfermented)"
msgstr[0] "醬油（未發酵）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soy sauce (unfermented)', 'str_pl': 'soy sauce
#. (unfermented)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "If fermented in a vat for 3 days, it will make fine soy sauce."
msgstr "如果在桶中發酵3天，就能製成優質醬油。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "miso (unripe)"
msgid_plural "miso (unripe)"
msgstr[0] "味噌（未熟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'miso (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'miso (unripe)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "The Miso's aging was successful!"
msgstr "味噌的熟化成功了！"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'miso (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'miso
#. (unripe)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Miso is aged."
msgstr "味噌已熟化。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'miso (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'miso (unripe)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Miso in the middle of aging. If left alone, it will be ferment in 8 days."
msgstr "正在熟化中的味噌。如果放置不管，它將在8天內發酵完成。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "miso"
msgid_plural "miso"
msgstr[0] "味噌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'miso', 'str_pl': 'miso'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Miso that has been matured. This food was treated as a health food during "
"the edo period."
msgstr "已熟化的味噌。這種食物在江戶時期被視為健康食品。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soy milk"
msgid_plural "soy milk"
msgstr[0] "豆漿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soy milk', 'str_pl': 'soy milk'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Squeezed soybeans. This looks like milk. But because it lacks fat, it can "
"not replace milk."
msgstr "榨取的大豆。這看起來像牛奶。但由於缺乏脂肪，它不能替代牛奶。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "okara"
msgid_plural "okara"
msgstr[0] "豆渣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'okara', 'str_pl': 'okara'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "The remnants of soy milk. Has a sweet taste."
msgstr "豆漿的殘渣。味道甜美。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "tofu"
msgid_plural "tofu"
msgstr[0] "豆腐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tofu', 'str_pl': 'tofu'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A traditional japanese mainstay. Solidified soy milk."
msgstr "日本傳統的主食。凝固的豆漿。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "aburage"
msgid_plural "aburage"
msgstr[0] "油揚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'aburage', 'str_pl': 'aburage'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Aburaage, also known as usu-age, is a type of Japanese deep-fried tofu (bean"
" curd)."
msgstr "油揚，也稱為薄揚，是一種日本油炸豆腐。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "unohana"
msgid_plural "unohana"
msgstr[0] "卯之花"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'unohana', 'str_pl': 'unohana'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Stir-fried okara with vegetables and shiitake mushroom. Delicious and sweet."
msgstr "用蔬菜和香菇炒制的豆渣。美味且甜美。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "natto"
msgid_plural "natto"
msgstr[0] "納豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'natto', 'str_pl': 'natto'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Fermented soybeans using Bacillus natto. A mainstay of Japanese cuisine."
msgstr "使用納豆芽孢桿菌發酵的大豆。日本料理的主食。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "natto (unripe)"
msgid_plural "natto (unripe)"
msgstr[0] "納豆（未熟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'natto (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'natto (unripe)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Now that's a unique smell! done!"
msgstr "這味道真獨特！完成了！"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'natto (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'natto
#. (unripe)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Currently fermenting."
msgstr "正在發酵中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'natto (unripe)', 'str_pl': 'natto (unripe)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Wrapped in soybeans. There are already natto bacteria in the beans, thus it "
"is not necessary add any additional bacteria. It is only safe to leave them "
"out for one day."
msgstr "包裹在大豆中。豆中已有納豆菌，因此無需額外添加細菌。僅可安全放置一天。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "dried natto"
msgid_plural "dried natto"
msgstr[0] "幹納豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dried natto', 'str_pl': 'dried natto'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Special product of Ibaraki mixed with natto. The natto is sun-dried to "
"enable long-term storage. The bacteria does not die when sun-dried alone, "
"does not die when boiled, and does it die from high concentration radiation."
" Like little waterbears."
msgstr "茨城縣特產混合納豆。納豆經日曬乾燥以便長期儲存。單獨日曬不會殺死細菌，煮沸不會殺死，高濃度輻射也不會殺死。就像小水熊蟲一樣。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "miso soup"
msgid_plural "miso soup"
msgstr[0] "味噌湯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'miso soup', 'str_pl': 'miso soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Japanese-style soup with miso. Eat with plenty of vegetables."
msgstr "日式味噌湯。搭配大量蔬菜食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "natto soup"
msgid_plural "natto soup"
msgstr[0] "納豆湯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'natto soup', 'str_pl': 'natto soup'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Miso soup with natto added. Looks good for you, but isn't particularly."
msgstr "加入納豆的味噌湯。看起來不錯，但實際上並不特別。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sealed bottle (miso soup)"
msgid_plural "sealed bottles (miso soup)"
msgstr[0] "密封瓶（味噌湯）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'sealed bottle (miso soup)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. bottles (miso soup)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'sealed bottle (natto soup)', 'str_pl':
#. 'sealed bottles (natto soup)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "You opened the lid of the sealed bottle, exposing the contents."
msgstr "你打開了密封瓶的蓋子，露出了裡面的內容物。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sealed bottle (miso soup)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. bottles (miso soup)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A sealed glass jar containing miso soup. Edible after opening the lid."
msgstr "一個裝有味噌湯的密封玻璃罐。打開蓋子後即可食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sealed bottle (natto soup)"
msgid_plural "sealed bottles (natto soup)"
msgstr[0] "密封瓶（納豆湯）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sealed bottle (natto soup)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. bottles (natto soup)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A sealed glass jar containing natto soup. You can eat if you open the lid."
msgstr "一個裝有納豆湯的密封玻璃罐。打開蓋子後即可食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Tofu hamburger"
msgid_plural "Tofu hamburgers"
msgstr[0] "豆腐漢堡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tofu hamburger', 'str_pl': 'Tofu hamburgers'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A baked patty of tofu and milled flour. A juicy morsel for all vegetarians."
msgstr "用豆腐和麵粉烘烤而成的肉餅。為所有素食者提供的多汁美味。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "tofu cheeseburger"
msgid_plural "tofu cheeseburgers"
msgstr[0] "豆腐芝士漢堡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tofu cheeseburger', 'str_pl': 'tofu
#. cheeseburgers'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A tofu hamburger with cheese."
msgstr "加了芝士的豆腐漢堡。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Tofu hamburger patty"
msgid_plural "Tofu hamburger patties"
msgstr[0] "豆腐漢堡肉餅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tofu hamburger patty', 'str_pl': 'Tofu hamburger
#. patties'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Just a round of tofu and flour. Bake and eat."
msgstr "只是一塊豆腐和麵粉的圓餅。烘烤後食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "vacuum pack (tofu hamburger patty)"
msgid_plural "vacuum packs (tofu hamburger patty)"
msgstr[0] "真空包裝（豆腐漢堡肉餅）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'vacuum pack (tofu hamburger patty)',
#. 'str_pl': 'vacuum packs (tofu hamburger patty)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'vacuum pack (natto bread)', 'str_pl': 'vacuum
#. packs (natto bread)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "You open the vacuum pack, exposing the contents."
msgstr "你打開了真空包裝，露出了裡面的內容物。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vacuum pack (tofu hamburger patty)', 'str_pl':
#. 'vacuum packs (tofu hamburger patty)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A vacuum pack of plastic packaging containing tofu hamburger patties. Bake "
"after opening it."
msgstr "一個裝有豆腐漢堡肉餅的塑料真空包裝。打開後烘烤食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "triple tofu burger"
msgid_plural "triple tofu burgers"
msgstr[0] "三重豆腐漢堡"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'triple tofu burger', 'str_pl': 'triple tofu
#. burgers'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A legendary item off the menu of the burger chain sozai official name: "
"triple toast."
msgstr "漢堡連鎖店sozai官方菜單上的傳奇物品：三重吐司。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soymilk cheese"
msgid_plural "soymilk cheese"
msgstr[0] "豆漿芝士"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soymilk cheese', 'str_pl': 'soymilk cheese'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Cheese made from soy milk. Not as rich as normal cheese, but refreshing "
"none-the-less."
msgstr "用豆漿製成的芝士。不如普通芝士濃郁，但依然清爽。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'koji', 'str_pl': 'koji'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A food made in the Heian period. The alkali of wood ash kills only bacteria "
"that prefer potassium and phosphorus."
msgstr "一種平安時代製作的食物。草木灰的鹼性只殺死偏好鉀和磷的細菌。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "koji (immature)"
msgid_plural "koji (immature)s"
msgstr[0] "麴黴（未成熟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'koji (immature)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Culture complete! done!"
msgstr "培養完成！完成！"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'koji (immature)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Culturing koji."
msgstr "正在培養麴黴。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'koji (immature)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Rice bran to grow on steamed rice and soybeans. Mixing wood ash is a recipe "
"using Singa from the Heian period. Considered the best way to obtain proper "
"bean sprouts."
msgstr "米糠用於在蒸米和大豆上生長。混合草木灰是使用平安時代新芽的配方。被認為是獲得合適豆芽的最佳方法。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "zunda"
msgid_plural "zunda"
msgstr[0] "毛豆泥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zunda', 'str_pl': 'zunda'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A ground of edamame. Becomes the raw material of zunder sweets."
msgstr "毛豆的研磨物。成為毛豆甜點的原料。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "kinako"
msgid_plural "kinako"
msgstr[0] "黃豆粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kinako', 'str_pl': 'kinako'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Mashed soybean. Becomes the raw material of Japanese sweets."
msgstr "搗碎的大豆。成為日式甜點的原料。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mirin"
msgid_plural "mirin"
msgstr[0] "味醂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mirin', 'str_pl': 'mirin'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Miso. One of the seasonings that adds sweet and sour taste to Japanese food."
msgstr "味噌。為日式食物增添酸甜味的調味料之一。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "mirin (unfermented)"
msgid_plural "mirin (unfermented)"
msgstr[0] "味醂（未發酵）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mirin (unfermented)', 'str_pl': 'mirin
#. (unfermented)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Becomes miso when it is aged. Takes about 70 hours to ferment."
msgstr "陳化後成為味噌。發酵大約需要70小時。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "nikujaga"
msgid_plural "nikujaga"
msgstr[0] "肉じゃが"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nikujaga', 'str_pl': 'nikujaga'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Japanese food that is said to have been made by a certain famous naval "
"general. It is quite sweet."
msgstr "據說是由某位著名海軍將領製作的日式食物。相當甜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sealed jar (nikujaga)"
msgid_plural "sealed jars (nikujaga)"
msgstr[0] "密封罐（肉じゃが）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'sealed jar (nikujaga)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. jars (nikujaga)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'sealed jar (soymilk stew)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. jars (soymilk stew)'}.
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "You open the lid of the sealed bottle, exposing the contents."
msgstr "你打開密封瓶的蓋子，暴露了裡面的內容物。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sealed jar (nikujaga)', 'str_pl': 'sealed jars
#. (nikujaga)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A sealed glass jar containing meat and potatoes. Eatable after the lid is "
"opened."
msgstr "一個裝有肉和土豆的密封玻璃罐。打開蓋子後即可食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "boiled edamame"
msgid_plural "boiled edamame"
msgstr[0] "煮毛豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled edamame', 'str_pl': 'boiled edamame'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Boiled green soybeans."
msgstr "煮熟的青大豆。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "inari"
msgid_plural "inari"
msgstr[0] "稻荷壽司"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inari', 'str_pl': 'inari'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A rice ball wrapped in sweetened fried rice."
msgstr "用甜味炸飯包裹的飯糰。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "yuba"
msgid_plural "yuba"
msgstr[0] "腐竹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'yuba', 'str_pl': 'yuba'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Boiling soymilk changes the surface into a film. This is called the Ramsden "
"phenomenon."
msgstr "煮沸豆漿使其表面形成一層薄膜。這被稱為蘭斯登現象。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "grilled yuba"
msgid_plural "grilled yuba"
msgstr[0] "烤腐竹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grilled yuba', 'str_pl': 'grilled yuba'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dish made out of grilled yuba. Yuba no Yakiyaki (grilled eel) and Seto bou"
" (pickles)."
msgstr "用烤腐竹製作的菜餚。腐竹燒（烤鰻魚）和瀨戶棒（醃菜）。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "soymilk stew"
msgid_plural "soymilk stew"
msgstr[0] "豆漿燉菜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'soymilk stew', 'str_pl': 'soymilk stew'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "It is a stew made based on soymilk."
msgstr "這是一種以豆漿為基礎的燉菜。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "sealed jar (soymilk stew)"
msgid_plural "sealed jars (soymilk stew)"
msgstr[0] "密封罐（豆漿燉菜）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sealed jar (soymilk stew)', 'str_pl': 'sealed
#. jars (soymilk stew)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A sealed glass jar containing soymilk stew. Eatable once the lid is opened."
msgstr "一個裝有豆漿燉菜的密封玻璃罐。打開蓋子後即可食用。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "natto bread"
msgid_plural "natto bread"
msgstr[0] "納豆麵包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'natto bread', 'str_pl': 'natto bread'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Bread containing natto."
msgstr "含有納豆的麵包。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "vacuum pack (natto bread)"
msgid_plural "vacuum packs (natto bread)"
msgstr[0] "真空包裝（納豆麵包）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vacuum pack (natto bread)', 'str_pl': 'vacuum
#. packs (natto bread)'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A vacuum pack of plastic packaging containing natto bread. Eatable once "
"opened."
msgstr "一個裝有納豆麵包的塑料真空包裝。打開後即可食用。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "straw pack"
msgid_plural "straw packs"
msgstr[0] "稻草包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'straw pack', 'str_pl': 'straw packs'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid "It is a mochi which wrapped natto. Reusable."
msgstr "這是一種包裹著納豆的麻糬。可重複使用。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "Flowerpot (developing green soybeans)"
msgid_plural "Flowerpots (developing green soybeans)"
msgstr[0] "花盆（培育中的毛豆）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Flowerpot (developing green soybeans)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (developing green soybeans)'}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "Edamame is ripe!"
msgstr "毛豆成熟了！"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'Flowerpot (developing green
#. soybeans)', 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (developing green soybeans)'}.
#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'Flowerpot (during soybean
#. cultivation)', 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (during soybean cultivation)'}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "It's growing up quickly."
msgstr "它長得很快。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flowerpot (developing green soybeans)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (developing green soybeans)'}
#: .\melee.json
msgid "It is a flowerpot that is raising edamame."
msgstr "這是一個正在培育毛豆的花盆。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "Flowerpot (Edamame)"
msgid_plural "Flowerpots (Edamame)"
msgstr[0] "花盆（毛豆）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flowerpot (Edamame)', 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots
#. (Edamame)'}
#: .\melee.json
msgid "It is a flowerpot where edamame has grown."
msgstr "這是一個毛豆已經長成的花盆。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "Flowerpot (during soybean cultivation)"
msgid_plural "Flowerpots (during soybean cultivation)"
msgstr[0] "花盆（大豆種植期間）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Flowerpot (during soybean cultivation)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (during soybean cultivation)'}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "Soy has been produced!"
msgstr "大豆已經產出！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flowerpot (during soybean cultivation)',
#. 'str_pl': 'Flowerpots (during soybean cultivation)'}
#: .\melee.json
msgid "It is a plant pot that grows soybeans."
msgstr "這是一個種植大豆的植物盆。"

#: .\melee.json
